Led by Devin Booker’s 34 PTS, 7 REB and 8 AST, the Phoenix Suns defeated the Los Angeles Lakers, 99-90, in Game 1. localize.description:
湖人队对阵太阳队 | 全场比赛花絮 | 2021年5月23日
